latestIgtvVideos.title: MEDISIA ASTHETIC CLINIC X THE BOHEMIAN GIRL
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
A lot of you must be dealing with your skin problems & wondering what to do with it.! well, don't worry. @medisiaaesthetic  got your back with their SKIN GYM TREATMENT. This is just a glimpse of what the treatment looks like. It varies upon different skin problems. You can visit their clinic & get your skin consulted with their doctors & know which treatment is best for your skin & move forward with the treatment. 
One treatment is far better than thousands of rupees you spend on costly cosmetics & beauty creams
. . 
Shot & edited by @mehuldabhade_ . .
